		<h1 class="title">他为什么会给通用CEO发邮件说，“我想并购你的公司”？</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Billl Vlasic</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-28 08:19:09 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
