<div class="com-share" data-id="10043" data-title="《他为什么会给通用CEO发邮件说，“我想并购你的公司”？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/10043/medium/10043.jpg?1436652469" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/10043.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
